The man with a physical challenge, Monday Itu who danced so well on his child’s dedication with his wife has finally received a wheelchair from a good Samaritan in church. The dedication took place at Saint or St’ Luke’s African Church in Agbarho, Ughelli North, Delta State, penultimate Sunday. In the trending video, Itu and his wife were seen dancing for their child’s dedication. When the man got to the altar, he began to dance with his strength. A few members in the church came out to celebrate him as they sprayed some cash on him. While spraying some cash on him, he continued dancing to the admiration of all According to reports, Itu who is well known in the church has been gifted a new wheelchair by a good Samaritan Monday and his wife are blessed with two children.